<section>
<section id="slide-orgeab61df">
<h2 id="orgeab61df">Backlash effect</h2>
<ul>
<li>Women experience negative reactions when they engage in "male" behavior</li>
<li>In this case, are females punished for using "male" words in their resumes?</li>

</ul>

</section>
</section>
<section>
